20%E2%80%94%20another%20topic%20that's%20wrought%20with%20unsolicited%20opinions).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20am%20truly%20introspective%2C%20I%20also%20think%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhilary-duff-just-announced-shes-pregnant-with-her-third-child-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20third%20child%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20way%20to%20break%20and%20check%20in%20on%20my%20priorities.%20It%20may%20sound%20counterintuitive%2C%20given%20that%20caring%20for%20a%20newborn%20isn't%20exactly%20a%20quiet%20or%20easy%20time%2C%20but%20hear%20me%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ddd2350b-38b7-469c-9b54-f46b9d3c3350%5C%22%3EI%20get%20to%20take%20a%20pause%20from%20the%20corporate%20world%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMaternity%20leave%20creates%20a%20forced%20and%20necessary%20pause%20in%20the%20hustle%20of%20corporate%20life.%20It's%20certainly%20not%20a%20vacation%2C%20but%20in%20my%20experience%2C%20maternity%20leave%20allowed%20me%20to%20step%20off%20the%20corporate%20hamster%20wheel%2C%20at%20least%20for%20a%20moment%2C%20and%20reset%20and%20reaffirm%20my%20life%20and%20career%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20my%20first%20son's%20birth%2C%20I%20recall%20actively%20giving%20myself%20space%20to%20decide%20if%20I%20would%20want%20to%20be%20a%20stay-at-home%20mom.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20discussed%20that%20our%20lifestyle%20and%20budget%20would've%20had%20to%20drastically%20change%20had%20I%20made%20that%20decision%2C%20but%20I%20also%20didn't%20know%20how%20becoming%20a%20mom%20might%20change%20me.%20How%20could%20I%20predict%20such%20a%20thing%3F%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20few%20months%20into%20maternity%20leave%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20needed%20the%20fulfillment%20of%20a%20career%20to%20feel%20like%20a%20whole%20human.%20Giving%20myself%20the%20space%20to%20explore%20that%20choice%20in%20those%20early%20days%20may%20be%20the%20reason%20I%20feel%20less%20guilt%20about%20being%20a%20working%20parent%20today.%20I%20actively%20chose%20these%20