0to%20quietly%20build%20large%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20Warren%20Buffett%2C%20people%20tend%20to%20follow%20your%20lead.%20And%20if%20they%20were%20to%20catch%20even%20a%20whiff%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eyou're%20building%20a%20large%20stake%20in%20a%20company%2C%20copycat%20traders%20could%20spark%20a%20premature%20price%20spike%20and%20make%20your%20purchase%20more%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBerkshire's%20assets%20may%20be%20worth%20over%20%241%20trillion%2C%20but%20Buffett%20still%20likes%20a%20good%20bargain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20that%20May%20filing%2C%20his%20mystery%20bet%20has%20been%20the%20talk%20of%20Wall%20Street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECould%20it%20be%20FedEx%3F%20UPS%3F%20Caterpillar%3F%20I%20bet%20it's%20Caterpillar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett's%20headline%20move%20last%20quarter%20was%20a%20%241.6%20billion%20bet%20on%20an%20industry%20that%20is%20home%20to%20something%20he%20once%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20tapeworm%20of%20American%20economic%20competitiveness.%26quot%3B%20He%20bought%20more%20than%205%20million%20shares%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-short-michael-burry-stock-portfolio-alibaba-meta-unitedhealth-buffett-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUnitedHealth.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnitedHealth's%20stock%20had%20plummeted%20since%20its%20CEO%2C%20Brian%20Thompson%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fda-says-luigi-mangione-terrorist-because-unitedhealthcare-execs-felt-terrorized-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efatally%20shot%20in%20December%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Along%20with%20other%20major%20US%20health%20insurers%2C%20the%20company%20has%20also%20been%20grappling%20with%20an%20unexpected%20rise%20in%20medical%20costs.%20In%20April%2C%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funitedhealth-q1-earnings-cut-outlook-medicare-alignment-stock-selloff-insurance-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3