to%20squeeze%20through%20the%20space%20it%20had%20and%20carefully%20inched%20forward%20%E2%80%94%20almost%20as%20if%20it%20was%20telling%20the%20other%20cars%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20make%20my%20left%20turn%2C%20darn%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Waymo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689bb691cfc04e97619b4cfa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Waymo%20drove%20through%20a%20line%20of%20cars%20waiting%20behind%20a%20bus%20to%20make%20a%20left%20turn%20out%20of%20a%20parking%20lot.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Waymos%20got%20my%20pickup%20and%20drop-off%20location%20exactly%20right%20every%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20times%20in%20San%20Francisco%20when%20a%20Waymo%20might%20pick%20me%20up%20about%20a%20block%20away%20from%20where%20I%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20multiple%20Waymo%20rides%20from%20early%20morning%20hours%20to%20Austin's%205%20p.m.%20peak%20traffic%20time.%20The%20average%20price%20across%C2%A0eight%20rides%20was%20%2410.69.%20The%20average%20pick-up%20time%20was%20about%20seven%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Austin%2C%20users%20must%20opt%20in%20for%20the%20autonomous%20vehicle%20option%20in%20their%20Uber%20app.%20There%20is%20no%20way%20to%20specifically%20request%20a%20robotaxi%20for%20each%20ride.%20Uber%20will%20instead%20pair%20you%20with%20whatever%20vehicle%20is%20on%20the%20most%20time-efficient%20route%20%E2%80%94%20human%20or%20robot%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Waymo%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20side-by-side%20screenshots%20of%20the%20Uber%20app.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689ba368194a2d49b8ae7205%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Uber%20app%20in%20Austin%20allows%20users%20to%20pair%20with%20a%20Waymo%20robotaxi.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20said%20Uber%20will%20likely%20send%20a%20human%20driver%20if%20the%20best%20route%20requires%20a%20highway.%20Waymo%20is%20testing%20on%20highways%20in%20SF%2C%20LA%2C%20and%20Phoenix%2C%20but%20public%20riders%20don't%20have%20access%20yet%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20canceling%2047%20Uber%20rides%20in%20my%20attempt%20to%20hail%20a%20Waymo%20so%20that%20I%20could%20recreate%20a%20route%20I%20took%20in%20Tesla's%20Robotaxi%20from%20Austin's%20South%20Congress%20area%20to%20the%20Crestview%20neighborhood%20up%20north%2C%20about%20nine%20miles%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20not%20end%20up%20connecting%20with%20a%20Waymo%20for%20that%20specific%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENormally%2C%20I%20don't%20mind%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobotaxis-change-role-of-human-drivers-uber-chief-says-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehuman%20Uber%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20main%20concern%20is%20getting%20from%20point%20A%20to%20B%20as%20quickly%2C%20safely%2C%20and%20cheaply%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20folks%20who%20want%20a%20robotaxi%20or%20would%20prefer%20a%20ride%20to%20themselves%2C%20I%20can%20see%20a%20scenario%20in%20the%20future%20where%20people%20will%20go%20straight%20to%20Tesla's%20Robotaxi%20app%20instead%20of%20Uber%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%2C%20once%20it's%20available%20to%20the%20general%20public%20and%20Tesla%20removes%20its%20safety%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224051e1fc-821e-46a3-b602-505f08490195%5C%22%3ETesla%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20Robotaxi%20fleet%20is%20made%20up%20of%20the%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-model-y%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EModel%20Y%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20I%20found%20to%20be%20a%20smooth%2C%20comfortable%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20hailed%20Teslas%20thro