0to%20be%20stuck%2C%20the%20remote%20agent%20said%20they'd%20help%20us%20out.%20We%20were%20soon%20on%20our%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20robotaxi%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6896452bcfc04e97619b2151%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla's%20Robotaxis%20are%20embalzoned%20with%20the%20%26quot%3BRobotaxi%26quot%3B%20logo%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20Model%20Ys.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%2F%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20intervention%20came%20about%2020%20minutes%20later%2C%20after%20we%20changed%20the%20route%20mid-journey.%20As%20we%20were%20heading%20down%20Fruth%20Street%2C%20Tesla's%20Robotaxi%20began%20to%20approach%20a%20road%20clearly%20marked%20with%20two%20%26quot%3BDo%20Not%20Enter%26quot%3B%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20I%20realized%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20importance%20of%20having%20a%20human%20safety%20monitor%20inside%20every%20car%20%E2%80%94%20and%20why%20the%20monitors%20appear%20to%20be%20on%20a%20strict%20do-not-talk-to-the-riders%20policy.%20Chatting%20might%20make%20the%20ride%20feel%20less%20awkward%2C%20but%20they're%20actually%20performing%20an%20important%20job%2C%20which%20is%20paying%20close%20attention%20to%20what's%20happening%20on%20the%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20car%20moved%20forward%2C%20the%20safety%20monitor%20touched%20a%20button%20on%20the%20center%20console%20screen%20to%20stop%20the%20ride.%20We%20were%20heading%20down%20an%20empty%20one-way%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221206%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20touches%20a%20button%20on%20the%20center%20console%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689e3d00194a2d49b8ae97a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22905%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Tesla%20Robotaxi%20safety%20monitor%20touches%20a%20button%20on%20the%20screen%20that%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BStop%20In%20Lane%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20car%20headed%20down%20a%20one-way%20road.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20remote%20support%20agent%20connected%20again%2C%20and%20the%20Robotaxi%20began%20a%20three-point%20turn%20before%20slamming%20the%20brakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20no%20other%20notable%20incidents%20on%20that%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20intervention%20came%20the%20next%20day.%20Kong%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20take%20the%20car%20to%20the%20very%20edge%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-new-robotaxi-geofence-austin-shape-elon-musk-bigger-waymo-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETesla's%20geofence%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20establishes%20the%20boundaries%20of%20the%20Robotaxi%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20changed%20the%20destination%20toward%20the%20end%20of%20our%20ride%2C%20the%20Tesla%20started%20to%20take%20us%20on%20a%20new%20route%20that%20briefly%20put%20us%20outside%20the%20geofence.%20A%20remote%20support%20agent%20called%20to%20let%20us%20know%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20they%20had%20to%20reroute%20the%20car%20so%20that%20it%20wouldn't%20go%20outside%20the%20digital%20boundaries.%20I%20was%20at%20least%20comforted%20to%20see%20how%20responsive%20the%20remote%20agents%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20Robotaxi%20also%20avoided%20the%20highway%20during%20my%20rides.%20It's%20unclear%20if%20Tesla%20is%20avoiding%20them%20for%20public%20riders%20for%20now%2C%20just%20as%20with%20Waymo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20fourth%20ride%20to%20North%20Austin%2C%20Kong%2C%20a%20five-year%20resident%20of%20Texas%2C%20noticed%20that%20the%20Robotaxi%20was%20taking%20a%20longer%20route%20to%20a%20destination%20that%20should've%20been%20an%2018-minute%20trip%20if%20the%20car%20had%20taken%20the%2035%20highway%20or%20MoPac%20Expressway%2C%20according%20to%20Google%20Maps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221206%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Back%20of%20the%20Tesla%20Robotaxi%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689e3e1c194a2d49b8ae97df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22905%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20ride%20in%20a%20Tesla%20Robotaxi%20had%20a%2031-minute%20arrival%20time%20for%20a%20trip%20that%20typically%20takes%20less%20than%2020%20minutes%2C%20according%20to%20Google%20Maps.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETraffic%20was%20light%20to%20moderate%20during%20the%20times%20I%20took%20Tesla's%20Robotaxi.%20There%20were%20no%20issues%20with%20pick-up%20or%20drop-off%20locations.%20Pick-up%20times%20were%20mostly%20around%2010%20minutes%2C%20but%20there%20was%20one%20case%20where%20the%20pick-up%20time%20was%20nearly%20half%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20hasn't%20specified%20how%20many%20cars%20it%20has%20added%20since%20it%20expanded%20the%20coverage%20area%2C%20but%20during%20the%20company's%20latest%20earnings%20call%20on%20July%2023%2C%20Ashok%20Elluswamy%2C%20Tesla's%20VP%20of%20AI%20software%2C%20said%20it%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bhandful%26quot%3B%20of%20vehicles%20on%20the%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20have%20direct%20access%20to%20the%20Robotaxi%20app%2C%20but%20based%20on%20what%20I%20saw%20from%20Kong%2C%20it%20appeared%20easy%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20glitched%20once%20and%20showed%20that%20a%20Robotaxi%20was%20on%20the%20way%2C%20even%20though%20we%20had%20just%20been%20dropped%20off%20at%20our%20destination.%20Kong%20told%20me%20that%20the%20app%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20buggy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22318a0d21-89ed-4c0b-9708-8d5e9f9b5065%5C%22%3EThe%20verdict%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20in%20our%20May%20test%20between%20Waymo%20and%20Tesla%20FSD%20(Supervised)%2C%20Waymo%20won.%20While%20impressive%2C%20Tesla's%20Robotaxi%20is%20still%20a%20work%20in%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20felt%20in%20danger%20while%20riding%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20didn't%20quite%20feel%20like%20the%20well-oiled%20service%20that%20Waymo%20delivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20intervention%20I%20experienced%20when%20Tesla's%20Robotaxi%20started%20driving%20down%20a%20one-way%20road%20showed%20why%20a%20safety%20monitor%20is%20still%20necessary.%20They're%20not%20passive%20passengers%2C%20but%20constantly%20watching%20for%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20suggest%20Waymo%20is%20perfect.%20Even%20after%20one%20hundred%20million%20autonomously%20driven%20miles%2C%20Waymo%20still%20makes%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Waymo%20on%20the%20road%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68951b71cfc04e97619b1174%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Waymo%20is%20stalled%20at%20an%20intersection%20in%20Downtown%20Austin.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Johan%20Pimentel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20previous%20Business%20Insider%20analysis%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-paid-rides-collision-increased-data-california-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWaymo's%20progress%20in%20California%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20between%20January%20and%20March%202025%2C%20when%20it%20provided%20more%20than%201.8%20million%20rides%20in%20the%20Golden%20State%2C%20Waymo%20saw%207%20collisions%20per%20100%2C000%20rides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20company%20has%20published%20data%20showing%20a%20significant%20safety%20advantage%20over%20the%20average%20human%20driver.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Waymo%20said%20it's%20providing%20250%2C000%20paid%20trips%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaymo's%20achievement%20didn't%20happen%20overnight.%20Seven%20years%20ago%2C%20Alphabet%20launched%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-one-riders-open-up-about-their-self-driving-experiences-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eearly%20rider%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20giving%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20vetted%20riders%20access%20to%20Waymos%20with%20safety%20drivers%20inside%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20Tesla's%20ramp-up%20will%20be%20faster%20%E2%80%94%20a%20thousand%20robotaxis%20in%20Austin%20by%20the%20end%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20year.%20Still%2C%20I'm%20more%20interested%20in%20another%20milestone%3A%20When%20will%20they%20remove%20the%20in-car%20safety%20monitor%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-vs-waymo-robotaxi-autonomous-self-driving-test-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755256441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-vs-waymo-robotaxi-autonomous-self-driving-test-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Business%20Insider%20reporter%20Lloyd%20Lee%20took%20test%20rides%20in%20Tesla%20and%20Waymo%20autonomous%20taxis%20in%20Austin.%20Tesla's%20Robotaxi%20needed%20more%20human%20intervention.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20to%20set%20up%20task%20force%20for%20next-generation%20reforms%2C%20says%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755256408000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2025-08%2F15%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X630%2F1755226600-2368.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovt-task-force-next-gen-reforms-economic-overhaul-pm-modi-125081500929_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20announces%20a%20task%20force%20to%20revamp%20economic%20laws%2C%20cut%20compliance%20costs%2C%20and%20boost%20India's%20competitiveness%20as%20part%20of%20the%202047%20developed%20nation%20vision%22%2C%22author%22%3A