%2Ftrump-putin-alaska-summit-ukraine-war-peace-deal-us-russia-zelenskyy-125081500894_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20lived%20in%20my%20mother-in-law's%20freezing%20garage%20in%20Utah%20for%201.5%20years.%20It%20helped%20us%20save%20thousands%2C%20but%20I%20sometimes%20felt%20ashamed.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22couple%20with%20their%20dog%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689a63f8194a2d49b8ae5ee6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThea%20Atkinson%20(right)%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20their%20dog.%3Cp%3EKassidy%20Meinhardt%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOur%20rent%20was%20set%20to%20increase%20by%2050%25%20so%20instead%20we%20moved%20in%20with%20my%20mother-in-law.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHer%20garage%20was%20the%20only%20available%20space%2C%20so%20we%20cleaned%20it%20up%20and%20made%20it%20as%20homey%20as%20we%20could.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20were%20there%20for%201.5%20years%20until%20another%20opportunity%20came%20along.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20spent%20nearly%20two%20years%20living%20in%20his%20mother's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-turned-garage-into-rent-free-apartment-for-son-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egarage%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%24250%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20the%20cute%2C%20converted%20kind%20you%20see%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-diy-fail-fix-bathroom-wall-makeover-tape-marker-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDIY%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20string%20lights%20and%20space-saving%20hacks.%20I'm%20talking%20cement%20floors%2C%20cobwebs%20in%20the%20rafters%2C%20exposed%20insulation%2C%20and%20space%20heaters%20aimed%20directly%20at%20the%20bed%20just%20to%20get%20us%20through%20the%20winter%20of%202022-2023%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20Utah's%20heav