%223798%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAtkinson's%20husband%20with%20their%20dog%20in%20their%20garage%20home%20around%20Christmas.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Thea%20Atkinson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20holidays%2C%20we%20added%20some%20decorations%20and%20played%20fireplace%20YouTube%20videos%20on%20the%20TV%20for%20a%20cozy%2C%20albeit%20artificial%2C%20ambiance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aa2aa4e2-a53b-4e8c-a3dd-94500f0dfed3%5C%22%3EOur%20story%20isn't%20unique%2C%20and%20maybe%20that's%20what%20makes%20it%20so%20devastating%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpark-city-utah-over-the-top-luxury-wealth-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESummit%20County%2C%20Utah%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20where%20my%20husband%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20%E2%80%94%20the%20median%20home%20price%20as%20of%20January%20hovered%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sltrib.com%2Fnews%2F2025%2F03%2F29%2Fhome-prices-summit-wasatch%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%241.7%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20state.%20We're%20not%20looking%20for%20anything%20close%20to%20that%2C%20but%20instead%20hope%20for%20something%20near%20the%20%24450%2C000%20price%20range%2C%20which%20still%20feels%20like%20a%20stretch%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20be%20thinking%20that%20moving%20to%20a%20cheaper%20area%20could%20be%20the%20solution%2C%20but%20that%20would%20mean%20leaving%20the%20town%20and%20tight-knit%20community%20we%20want%20to%20raise%20a%20family%20in%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20trade%20we're%20not%20ready%20to%20make.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20came%20from%20a%20big%20Mormon%20family%20%E2%80%94%20the%20oldest%20of%20six%20children.%20We%20never%20wanted%20for%20love%20or%20food%20on%20the%20table%2C%20but%20when%20your%20parents%20are%20trying%20to%20stretch%20what%20they%20have%20between%20a%20gaggle%20of%20children%2C%20there's%20not%20much%20left%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%