e%20AI.%20OpenAI's%20latest%20move%20could%20help%20close%20the%20gap.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELast%20week%2C%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20announced%20GPT-oss%2C%20a%20family%20of%20large%20language%20models%20with%20%26quot%3Bopen%20weights.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnalysts%20weighed%20in%20on%20how%20the%20move%20could%20shift%20the%20US-China%20open-source%20AI%20race.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20been%20trailing%20China%20in%20the%20race%20for%20open-source%20AI.%20OpenAI's%20latest%20move%20could%20help%20close%20that%20gap%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20could%20also%20spur%20China%20to%20speed%20up%20its%20own%20releases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20OpenAI%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-gpt-oss-open-weight-llm-ai-model-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%20announced%20GPT-oss%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20family%20of%20large%20language%20models%20with%20%26quot%3Bopen%20weights.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20anyone%20can%20see%20or%20use%20information%20determining%20how%20the%20model%20works%20after%20it's%20been%20trained%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20the%20full%20source%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20this%20is%20the%20best%20and%20most%20usable%20open%20model%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20wrote%20on%20X%20on%20Aug%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGPT-oss%20is%20OpenAI's%20first%20open-weight%20language%20model%20in%20over%20five%20years%2C%20since%20the%20release%20of%20GPT-2%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de820d81-c683-4337-9fd7-4d5c10b39fa1%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20models%20'narrowed%20the%20gap'%20with%20China%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERay%20Wang%2C%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eresearch%20director%20for%20semiconductors%20and%20emerging%20technology%20at%20Futurum%20Group%2C%20said%20OpenAI's%20open-weight%20release%20was%20likely%20influenced%20by%20the%20strong%20reception%20for%20open-sourced%20Chinese%20models%20such%20as%20those%20from%20DeepSeek%2C%20whose%20release%20shook%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-startup-deepseek-openai-america-ai-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emarkets%20in%20January%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20said%20OpenAI's%20new%20models%20%26quot%3Bnarrowed%20the%20gap%26quot%3B%20with%20China%20thanks%20to%20their%20%26quot%3Bcompetitive%20performance%20benchmarks%20and%20sizes%20against%20their%20Chinese%20counterparts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20still%20maintains%20a%20slight%20lead%2C%20with%20a%20broader%2C%20higher%20number%20of%20competitive%20open-source%20models%20available%20in%20the%20market%20compared%20with%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-ai-models-manus-deepseek-alibaba-tencent-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChinese%20open-source%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%20include%20Alibaba's%20Qwen%20series%2C%20Baidu's%20ERNIE%204.5%2C%20and%20Moonshot's%20Kimi%20K2%2C%20alongside%20DeepSeek's%20recent%20V3%20and%20R1%20releases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20OpenAI's%20open-weight%20models%2C%20Chinese%20firms%20might%20respond%20by%20accelerating%20their%20own%20open-source%20releases%20to%20stay%20top%20of%20mind%20for%20developers%2C%20said%20Wei%20Sun%2C%20the%20principal%20analyst%20for%20AI%20at%20Counterpoint%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20they%20would%20aim%20for%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-deepseek-integrate-ai-consolidation-us-openai-paywall-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eecosystem%20lock-ins%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20with%20models%20integrated%20into%20dominant%20domestic%20platforms%20like%20Alipay%20and%20WeChat%20%26quot%3Bto%20monetize%20downstream%20rather%20than%20at%20the%20model%20layer%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWang%20said%20China's%20drive%20to%20%26quot%3Bpush%20the%20boundaries%20of%20open-source%20models%20will%20likely%20continue%20unabated%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BOpenAI's%20action%20may%20accelerate%20and%20motivate%20their%20efforts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229803d1a5-04ab-474d-a5fa-3ad832bcf70b%5C%22%3EWhy%20catching%20up%20matters%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20US%20doesn't%20close%20the%20gap%20in%20open-source%20AI%2C%20Chinese%20models%20could%20gain%20more%20momentum%20and%20become%20the%20default%20foundation%20for%20applications%20and%20research%20around%20the%20world%2C%20Wang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20American%20companies%2C%20that%20could%20be%20a%20problem%2C%20said%20Natham%20Lambert%2C%20a%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esenior%20research%20scientist%20at%20the%20Allen%20Institute%20for%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20the%20US%20doesn't%20invest%20in%20the%20open%20AI%20race%2C%20the%20standards%20by%20which%20AI%20is%20developed%20will%20become%20Chinese.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmerican%20companies%20will%20become%20secondary%20markets%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20primary%20beneficiary%20of%20AI%20progress%20as%20they%20have%20been%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20AI's%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20push%20in%20open%20source%20is%20also%20more%20than%20just%20sharing%20the%20latest%20technology%2C%20said%20Lian%20Jye%20Su%2C%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Echief%20analyst%20at%20Omdia%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20technology%20research%20and%20consulting%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20also%20about%20developer%20engagement%20and%20influence%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20way%20to%20escape%20the%20increasingly%20restrictive%20access%20to%20US%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20said%20in%20its%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-global-ai-regulation-trump-openai-meta-deepmind-anthropic-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmer