ws%2C%20with%20fans%20praising%20the%20lead%20actors'%20performances%20and%20labeling%20it%20a%20'mass%20entertainer.'%20On%20its%20opening%20day%2C%20'War%202'%20grossed%20%E2%82%B952.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Finding%20Dora%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Distorted%20images%20of%20a%20woman's%20face%20and%20a%20silhouette%20of%20a%20woman%20texting.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689cce93cfc04e97619b5ad3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%3B%20Rebecca%20Zisser%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMonths%20ago%2C%20Ahmet%20Tozal%20took%20out%20three%20credit%20card%20loans%20and%20withdrew%20his%20life%20savings%20to%20make%20a%20fortune%20off%20crypto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2044-year-old%20Turkish%20garment%20worker%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20Istanbul%20at%20the%20time%2C%20said%20he'd%20been%20goaded%20by%20a%20new%20friend%20who%20contacted%20him%20via%20a%20random%20WhatsApp%20message%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20claimed%20she'd%20messaged%20him%20accidentally%2C%20but%20was%20friendly%20and%20seemed%20interested%20in%20Turkey%2C%20Tozal%20said.%20She%20told%20him%20she%20was%20a%20wealthy%20businesswoman%20who%20would%20soon%20be%20visiting%20his%20country%20on%20holiday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETozal%20said%20she%20sent%20him%20dozens%20of%20photos%20of%20herself%2C%20a%20young%20East%20Asian%20woman%20traveling%20the%20world%20and%20attending%20prestigious%20conferences.%20He%20said%20they%20video-called%20once%2C%20for%20a%20few%20seconds.%20Eventually%2C%20she%20suggested%20he%20try%20investing%20in%20crypto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trajectory%20of%20their%20relationship%20has%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20what%20global%20authorities%20call%20a%20classic%20pig-butchering%20scam%2C%20typically%20run%20by%20gangs%20in%20Asia.%20Tozal%20said%20that%20over%20several%20weeks%2C%20the%20woman%20convinced%20him%20to%20invest%20about%20400%2C000%20Turkish%20lira%2C%20or%20a%20year's%20worth%20of%20his%20wages%2C%20into%20a%20cryptocurrency%20called%20UAI%20Coin.%20It%20never%20existed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETozal%20told%20me%20he%20lost%20everything.%20Saddled%20with%20debt%20and%20broke%2C%20Tozal%20moved%20alone%20to%20Uzbekistan%20to%20find%20a%20higher%20salary%20that%20could%20feed%20his%20family%20and%20pay%20off%20an%20extra%20200%2C000%20lira%20in%20loan%20interest.%20His%20wife%20and%20four%20children%20stayed%20behind%20in%20Turkey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20I%20think%20about%20it%2C%20it%20makes%20one%20almost%20go%20mad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me%20on%20a%20call%20from%20his%20shared%20apartment%20in%20Andijan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPig-butchering%2C%20a%20crypto%20scam%20that%20started%20in%20China%2C%20is%20now%20a%20global%20crisis.%20It%20draws%20its%20name%20from%20the%20concept%20of%20fattening%20a%20pig%20before%20slaughter%3A%20The%20purveyors%20build%20a%20relationship%20with%20a%20mark%20over%20weeks%20or%20months%20before%20persuading%20them%20to%20give%20away%20or%20invest%20large%20sums.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202024%20University%20of%20Texas%20study%20estimated%20that%20%2475%20billion%20has%20been%20lost%20to%20such%20schemes%20since%202020.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20Heartland%20Tri-State%20Bank%20in%20Kansas%20went%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F08%2F21%2Fcryptocurrency-shan-hanes-pig-butchering-scam.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebankrupt%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20its%20CEO%20poured%20%2447%20million%20of%20company%20cash%20into%20a%20similar%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETozal%20has%20little%20chance%20of%20recovering%20his%20money%2C%20and%20dozens%20of%20other%20men%20say%20they%20were%20fooled%20by%20the%20same%20scam.%20Betrayed%20and%20desperate%20for%20any%20restitution%20possible%2C%20they%20latched%20onto%20the%20only%20lead%20they%20could%20find%3A%20the%20woman%20behind%20the%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWho%20was%20she%3F%20Each%20of%20the%20men%20had%20photos%20and%20videos%20of%20her%2C%20the%20young%20East%20Asian%20woman%20who%20seemed%20to%20be%20living%20the%20high%20life%2C%20but%20not%20much%20else%20to%20go%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20hunted%20for%20answers%2C%20their%20stories%20of%20loss%20and%20grievance%20would%20come%20to%20haunt%20a%20person%20thousands%20of%20miles%20away%2C%20a%20millennial%20trying%20to%20make%20a%20name%20for%20herself%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20months%2C%20as%20he%20was%20lured%20into%20the%20crypto%20trap%2C%20Tozal%20knew%20her%20only%20as%20Dora.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20nine%20months%2C%20I%20spoke%20with%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20men%20from%20around%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20many%20in%20Central%20and%20West%20Asia%20%E2%80%94%20who%20say%20they've%20been%20affected%20by%20this%20specific%20pig-butchering%20scam.%20While%20their%20experiences%20varied%2C%20each%20one%20was%20tricked%20with%20the%20likeness%20of%20the%20same%20Asian%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeven%20of%20these%20men%2C%20including%20Tozal%2C%20agreed%20to%20full%20interviews.%20I%20verified%20all%20of%20their%20identities%2C%20and%20they%20showed%20me%20evidence%20of%20their%20online%20interactions.%20Several%20also%20showed%20me%20screenshots%20of%20their%20financial%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20were%20unwilling%20to%20be%20named%20and%20said%20they%20did%20not%20report%20their%20losses%20to%20the%20authorities%20for%20fear%20of%20being%20seen%20as%20fools%20and%20damaging%20their%20reputations.%20Some%20said%20they'd%20fallen%20in%20love%20with%20their%20WhatsApp%20acquaintance%3B%20Tozal%20said%20he%20and%20Dora%20were%20strictly%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshots%20show%20conversations%20with%20scam%20workers%20posing%20as%20women%20like%20%26quot%3BDora.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689d8ddf194a2d49b8ae8bcd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20men%20received%20cold%20texts%20from%20a%20woman%20claiming%20to%20have%20extensive%20experience%20in%20investments.%3Cp%3EScreenshots%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20men%20come%20from%20different%20companies%20and%20walks%20of%20life.%20The%20common%20denominator%3F%20They%20all%20had%20jobs%20and%20thus%20a%20source%20of%20cash.%20Aamy%20Ace%2C%20a%2044-year-old%20Indian%20pharmaceutical%20manufacturing%20worker%2C%20said%20he%20was%20cheated%20out%20of%20%2412%2C000%20meant%20for%20his%20father's%20cancer%20treatment.%20Another%20man%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20Kazakhstani%20restaurant%20manager%20in%20Almaty%20named%20Amir%2C%20said%20he%20borrowed%20and%20lost%20%248%2C000%20%E2%80%94%2010%20times%20his%20monthly%20salary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20remember%20different%20names.%20Some%20said%20they%20spoke%20to%20%26quot%3BJasmine%26quot%3B%20for%20weeks%2C%20while%20others%20knew%20her%20as%20%26quot%3BAnna.%26quot%3B%20Several%2C%20like%20Tozal%2C%20told%20me%20their%20contact%20was%20%26quot%3BDora.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20playbook%20for%20this%20scam%20is%20standardized.%20Men%20like%20Tozal%20would%20receive%20a%20cold%20text%20and%20slowly%20be%20persuaded%20to%20strike%20up%20a%20friendship%20or%20romance%20with%20the%20texter.%20All%20were%20sent%20photos%20of%20the%20same%20young%20Asian%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20very%20standard%20hook%20is%20an%20attractive%20person%2C%20male%20or%20female%2C%20coming%20in%20and%20saying%3A%20'Oh%20yeah%2C%20I%20have%20a%20business%20opportunity%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20come%20see%20you%20soon%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20Joshua%20James%2C%20a%20cybercrime%20coordinator%20in%20Bangkok%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20Office%20on%20Drugs%20and%20Crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20their%20contacts%20convinced%20them%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20fake%20asset.%20Most%20of%20the%20men%20said%20they%20put%20their%20money%20into%20a%20faux%20cryptocurrency%20called%20UAI%20Coin.%20A%20mobile%20app%20and%20fake%20trading%20website%20lent%20a%20sheen%20of%20legitimacy%20to%20the%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20the%20profits%20seemed%20eye-watering.%20Erdi%20Bilgi%C3%A7%2C%20a%2036-year-old%20Turkish%20electrician%20in%20Zonguldak%2C%20told%20me%20his%20initial%20%24100%20investment%20turned%20into%20%24500%20overnight%20in%20late%202023.%20Bilgi%C3%A7%2C%20calling%20himself%20an%20avid%20investor%2C%20said%20he%20tracks%20stock%20prices%20and%20bitcoin%20almost%20daily%2C%20and%20felt%20UAI%20Coin's%20prices%20moved%20in%20sync%20with%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20when%20he%20withdrew%20his%20initial%20gains%2C%20he%20received%20the%20full%20sum%20in%20his%20bank%20account.%20Emboldened%2C%20he%20took%20out%20a%20%241%2C500%20loan%20at%20Dora's%20behest%2C%20gathered%20his%20life's%20savings%20of%20about%20%2410%2C000%2C%20and%20put%20them%20all%20in%20UAI%20Coin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20told%20me%3A%20'Sell%20your%20car%2C%20sell%20this%2C%20sell%20that%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228f9f3ba5-eef5-44be-a7ee-f28f62b231d2%5C%22%3ELosing%20it%20all%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20Tozal%20and%20Bilgi%C3%A7%2C%20it%20seemed%20as%20though%20there%20was%20only%20one%20woman%20contacting%20them.%20But%20scam%20gangs%2C%20many%20based%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20are%20known%20to%20force%20human-trafficked%20victims%20to%20work%20in%20teams%2C%20sometimes%20with%20multiple%20people%20posing%20as%20the%20same%20woman%20in%20conversation%20with%20a%20mark.%20The%20US%20Institute%20of%20Peace%20estimated%20in%202024%20that%20some%20220%2C000%20trafficked%20victims%20are%20involved%20in%20scams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJudging%20by%20a%20lot%20of%20testimonies%20of%20survivors%20of%20human%20trafficking%20coming%20from%20scam%20compounds%2C%20many%20of%20them%20were%20being%20asked%20to%20pose%20as%20attractive%20young%20ladies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mina%20Chiang%2C%20founder%20of%20Humanity%20Research%20Consultancy%2C%20a%20UK-registered%20anti-trafficking%20social%20enterprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20their%20ploy%20more%20convincing%2C%20gangs%20have%20a%20woman%20take%20part%20in%20occasional%20video%20calls%20or%20voice%20messages.%20Several%20men%20in%20the%20Dora%20scam%20told%20me%20they%20received%20voice%20messages%20and%20forwarded%20them%20to%20me.%20A%20few%2C%20including%20Tozal%2C%20also%20said%20they%20had%20brief%20video%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20tactics%20helped%20to%20convince%20them%20that%20Dora%20was%20real%2C%20they%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20men's%20savings%20are%20invested%2C%20the%20critical%20point%20of%20the%20scam%20unfolds.%20The%20victims%20discover%20they%20can't%20withdraw%20their%20funds%2C%20and%20the%20scammers%20try%20squeezing%20them%20for%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETozal%20said%20he%20asked%20Dora%20for%20help%20and%20was%20directed%20to%20pay%20a%20tax-related%20fine%20to%20unlock%20his%20account.%20When%20that%20didn't%20work%2C%20he%20said%2C%20an%20engineer's%20fee%20was%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20knew%20then%20that%20he'd%20been%20fooled.%20The%20funds%20he%20lost%2C%20including%20his%20debt%2C%20are%20worth%20about%20%2415%2C000%20now%2C%20in%20a%20country%20where%20the%20average%20worker%20earns%20%247%2C300%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20what%20it%20is.%20My%20money%20is%20gone%2C%26quot%3B%20Tozal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20said%20they've%20lost%20even%20more.%20A%2050-year-old%20Turkish%20academic%20in%20Ankara%20said%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20had%20sold%20their%20apartment%20to%20save%20for%20a%20new%20city-center%20flat%20and%20dumped%20that%20money%2C%20along%20with%20%2450%2C000%20he%20convinced%20relatives%20to%20invest%2C%20into%20UAI%20Coin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20showed%20me%20a%20police%20report%20he%20made%20in%20Ankara%2C%20in%20which%20he%20reported%20losing%20more%20than%20%24100%2C000%20to%20the%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20asked%20myself%2C%20how%20am%20I%20going%20to%20live%3F%20I%20can%20survive%2C%20but%20I%20have%20a%20daughter%20in%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Now%2C%20he%20added%2C%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20are%20working%20weekends%20and%20second%20jobs%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d693b9da-166c-4015-885a-044216e12efb%5C%22%3EFinding%20Dora%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20spring%20of%202024%2C%20the%20group%20scamming%20Tozal%20appeared%20to%20make%20a%20mistake.%20As%20the%20men%20nursed%20their%20wounded%20pride%2C%20some%20received%20an%20email%20offering%20further%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221386%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20an%20email%20sent%20by%20scammers%20perpetuating%20the%20UAI%20Coin%20scam.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689d8adfcfc04e97619b64c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22724%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20sample%20email%20from%20the%20gang%20running%20the%20UAI%20Coin%20scam.%3Cp%3EScreenshot%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sender%20neglected%20to%20blind%20carbon%20copy%20each%20victim's%20email%20address%2C%20and%20the%20men%20began%20to%20contact%20each%20other.%20They%20gathered%20on%20WhatsApp%20groups%20and%20social%20media%2C%20swapping%20stories%20of%20how%20they'd%20been%20fooled%20by%20UAI%20Coin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20they%20realized%20they'd%20all%20been%20talking%20to%20the%20same%20woman.%20Younger%20ones%2C%20like%20Bilgi%C3%A7%20the%20electrician%2C%20put%20her%20photos%20into%20a%20reverse%20Google%20image%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20found%20someone.%20She%20wasn't%20Dora%2C%20or%20Jasmine%2C%20or%20Anna%3A%20Her%20name%20was%20Abe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20be%20sure%20100%25%20it's%20her%2C%20but%20the%20videos%20and%20photos%20that%20we%20saw%20online%20were%20consistent%2C%26quot%3B%20Bilgi%C3%A7%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbe%20is%20a%20Malaysian%20woman%2C%20they%20learned.%20She%20lives%20over%205%2C000%20miles%20from%20Tozal%20and%20Bilgi%C3%A7%20and%20runs%20a%20public%20Instagram%20account.%20Her%20name%20quickly%20spread%20among%20the%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20those%20like%20Tozal%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20the%20first%20real%20step%20to%20getting%20their%20money%20back.%20But%20as%20I%20soon%20discovered%2C%20this%20woman%20wasn't%20the%20mastermind%20of%20an%20audacious%20lonelyhearts%20scam%3B%20she%20was%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20victim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAbe%20Lim%20was%2020%20minutes%20late%20when%20we%20met%20at%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20in%20Kuala%20Lumpur's%20upscale%20shopping%20district.%20Traffic%20was%20crazy%20that%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20so%20sorry%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2029-year-old%2C%20sheepish%20as%20we%20shook%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELim%20was%20easy%20to%20find%20online%2C%20and%20once%20I%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20her%2C%20she%20was%20keen%20to%20talk.%20She%20has%20some%20175%2C000%20followers%20on%20Instagram%2C%20where%20she%20posts%20roughly%20twice%20or%20thrice%20a%20week%2C%20often%20glamour%20or%20fashion%20shots%20of%20herself.%20Lim%20told%20me%20her%20personal%20brand's%20focus%20is%20the%20climate%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDJzIVU7SuwY%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDJzIVU7SuwY%2F%3Futm_source%