2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20I've%20sort%20of%20put%20myself%20in%20the%20public%20spotlight%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20expected%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202024%2C%20she%20said%2C%20the%20men%20began%20contacting%20her%20friends%20and%20family%20and%20claiming%20she'd%20defrauded%20them%20out%20of%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars.%20There%20were%20rumors%20of%20self-harm%20or%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20like%2C%20OK%2C%20this%20is%20serious%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e9ab080-3f46-4711-b354-612f212b7bbd%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20year%20went%20on%2C%20Lim%20was%20trapped%20in%20an%20escalating%20online%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMessages%20flooded%20her%20inbox%20and%20Instagram%20comments.%20She%20said%20she%20received%20dozens%20of%20emails%20and%20texts%20a%20day%20and%20showed%20me%20several%20on%20her%20phone.%20Lim%20was%20all%20smiles%20in%20her%20interview%2C%20but%20her%20fatigue%20and%20frustration%20were%20palpable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20mentally%20draining%2C%26quot%3B%20Lim%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20heartbroken%20men%20tried%20to%20rekindle%20a%20nonexistent%20relationship%20with%20her%3B%20others%20sent%20threats%2C%20she%20said.%20For%20the%20first%20few%20months%20of%202024%2C%20she%20told%20me%2C%20she%20feared%20leaving%20her%20home%20in%20Malaysia.%20Lim%20now%20tries%20to%20delay%20her%20social%20media%20posts%20by%20a%20few%20days%20to%20keep%20her%20live%20location%20secret.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20messages%20that%20said%20like%3A%20'I'll%20fly%20down%20to%20kill%20you%2C%20track%20you%20down%20and%20make%20you%20pay%20for%20what%20you%20did%2C'%26quot%3B%20Lim%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20screenshots%20show%20messages%20from%20victims%20who%20blamed%20Lim%20for%20their%20losses.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689d832c194a2d49b8ae8b9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20men%20sent%20Lim%20multiple%20messages%20accusing%20her%20of%20stealing%20their%20money%2C%20while%20others%2C%20like%20in%20the%20screenshot%20on%20the%20right%2C%20reached%20out%20to%20her%20friends.%3Cp%3EAbe%20Lim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20men%20were%20divided%20on%20whether%20Lim%20was%20%26quot%3BDora%26quot%3B%20or%20an%20unwitting%20victim%20of%20someone%20pretending%20to%20be%20her.%20Some%2C%20like%20Bilgi%C3%A7%2C%20said%20she%20clearly%20wasn't%20the%20woman%20they%20had%20chatted%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20sent%20me%20recordings%20of%20their%20video%20calls%2C%20which%20showed%20East%20or%20Southeast%20Asian%20women%20holding%20up%20a%20hand%20or%20using%20a%20camera%20angle%20to%20obscure%20their%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInternet%20connection%20is%20not%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20woman%20in%20one%20video%20I%20viewed.%20She%20was%20clearly%20not%20Lim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fbde8036-b3b7-4373-a6de-ad414c7fc5a0%5C%22%3E'Should%20I%20compensate%20them%3F'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Lim%20and%20I%20sipped%20tea%20in%20Malaysia%2C%20she%20explained%20how%20she%20was%20grappling%20with%20a%20dilemma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20personal%20brand%20living%20on%20Instagram%2C%20how%20much%20time%20should%20she%20spend%20defending%20her%20reputation%20and%20speaking%20out%20against%20scams%3F%20Should%20she%20stop%20posting%3F%20Her%20brand%20was%20about%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%20not%20going%20to%20war%20against%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20platform%2C%20it's%20not%20that%20hard%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20do%20I%20want%20to%20be%20known%20as%20the%20person%20that%20combats%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202024%2C%20she%20posted%20several%20warnings%20about%20scams%20on%20Instagram.%20Some%20of%20the%20men%20were%20in