e-facility-justice-department-opposes-use-of-weapon-brush-judge-accuses-trump-admin-of-engaging-in-unconstitutional-game%2Farticleshow%2F123317185.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftoothbrush-ban-at-ice-facility-justice-department-opposes-use-of-weapon-brush-judge-accuses-trump-admin-of-engaging-in-unconstitutional-game%2Famp_articleshow%2F123317185.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftoothbrush-ban-at-ice-facility-justice-department-opposes-use-of-weapon-brush-judge-accuses-trump-admin-of-engaging-in-unconstitutional-game%2Famp_articleshow%2F123317185.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haryana%20Teacher%20Builds%20Rs%202%20Cr%20Honey%20Empire%2C%20Trains%20500%2B%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20gathered%20around%20Jagpal%20Singh%20Phogat%E2%80%99s%20farm%20in%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Jhajjar%20district%2C%20intrigued%20by%20the%20sight%20of%20bee%20boxes%20placed%20across%20his%20wheat%20fields.%20A%20teacher%20by%20profession%2C%20Jagpal%20deftly%20handled%20the%20buzzing%20boxes%2C%20drawing%20laughter%20from%20the%20onlookers%20%E2%80%94%20including%20his%20own%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20family%20opposed%20my%20decision%20to%20start%20beekeeping%2C%20especially%20my%20%3Cem%3Ebapu%20%3C%2Fem%3E(father).%20He%20sarcastically%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EArey%20master%2C%20gaay%20paal%20le%2C%20bhains%20paal%20le%2C%20bakri%20paal%20le%2C%20murgi%20paal%20le%2C%20makkhi%20ke%20pali%3F%20Ud%20javegi.%20%3C%2Fem%3E(You%20could%20have%20opted%20for%20cow%20rearing%20or%20buffaloes%2C%20poultry%2C%20or%20goat%20farming%2C%20why%20did%20you%20choose%20to%20raise%20bees%3F%20They%20will%20fly%20away)%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Jagpal%20as%20he%20recalls%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20beekeeping%20was%20an%20unfamiliar%20concept%20in%20their%20village.%20While%20many%20dismissed%20Jagpal%20as%20crazy%2C%20their%20views%20quickly%20changed%20when%20they%20witnessed%20the%20remarkable%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWithin%20a%20month%2C%20I%20managed%20to%20fill%20at%20least%2025%20large%20tin%20containers%20with%20honey%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Jagpal.%20%E2%80%9CUntil%20then%2C%20we%20had%20only%20seen%20honey%20in%20small%20bottles.%20Even%20my%20father%20was%20astonished%20and%20asked%20how%20much%20it%20could%20sell%20for.%20I%20told%20him%20each%20container%20was%20worth%20Rs%202%2C000.%20That%20was%20more%20than%20we%20could%20earn%20from%20six%20months%20of%20hard%20work%20on%20the%20wheat%20farm.%20Surprised%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Why%20didn%E2%80%99t%20you%20start%20this%20sooner%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-4-1733830341.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jaspal%20inspecting%20a%20bee%20frame%20near%20an%20open%20beehive%20box%2C%20surrounded%20by%20multiple%20beehive%20boxes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-4-1733830341.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-4-1733830341-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-4-1733830341-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-4-1733830341-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fhoney-business-4-1733830341-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388206%5C%22%20