tional%20purposes%20only)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20early%20morning%20at%20the%20Ramagundam%20reservoir%20in%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20Peddapalli%20district.%20The%20water%20is%20still%2C%20broken%20only%20by%20the%20occasional%20ripple%20of%20a%20passing%20bird.%20From%20the%20shore%2C%20you%20see%20something%20unusual%20%E2%80%94%20thousands%20of%20gleaming%20blue%20panels%20stretching%20far%20into%20the%20distance%2C%20quietly%20soaking%20up%20the%20sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20mirage.%20It%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20floating%20photovoltaic%20(FPV)%20plants%2C%20generating%20100%20megawatts%20(MW)%20of%20clean%20electricity%20without%20claiming%20an%20inch%20of%20farmland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20country%20like%20India%2C%20where%20every%20square%20metre%20of%20land%20is%20contested%20between%20farms%2C%20factories%2C%20and%20cities%2C%20this%20technology%20feels%20almost%20transformative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20does%20it%20work%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20simple%20idea%20behind%20floating%20solar%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20is%20elegantly%20simple%3A%20instead%20of%20fixing%20solar%20panels%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20you%20mount%20them%20on%20buoyant%20platforms%20and%20let%20them%20float%20on%20water%20bodies%20%E2%80%94%20reservoirs%2C%20lakes%2C%20industrial%20ponds%2C%20and%20irrigation%20canals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20approach%20delivers%20immediate%20benefits%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20land-use%20conflict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20It%20frees%20up%20land%20for%20agriculture%2C%20housing%2C%20or%20conservation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigher%20efficiency%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20cooling%20effect%20of%20water%20prevents%20overheating%2C%20boosting%20output%20by%20up%20to%2010%20percent%20compared%20to%20ground-mounted%20systems.%20This%20is%20because%20lower%20panel%20temperatures%20reduce%20electrical%20resistance%2C%20allowing%20more%20sunlight%20to%20be%20converted%20into%20electricity.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20water-stressed%20regions%2C%20FPV%20brings%20another%20bonus%3A%20panels%20shade%20the%20surface%2C%20slowing%20evaporation.%20Studies%20show%20a%20one-megawatt%20FPV%20plant%20can%20prevent%20more%20than%201%2C300%20cubic%20metres%20of%20water%20loss%20each%20year.%20At%20Ramagundam%2C%20the%20National%20Thermal%20Power%20Corporation%20(NTPC)%20plant%20is%20expected%20to%20save%20two%20billion%20litres%20annually%2C%20enough%20to%20meet%20the%20water%20needs%20of%2010%2C000%20households.%20Experts%20say%20this%20benefit%20is%20just%20one%20example%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fiit-guwahati-startup-floating-solar-plants-quant-solar-technologies-water-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eversatility%20of%20floating%20solar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20renewable%20energy%20expert%20Harsh%20Tiwari%2C%20founder%20of%20EMPBindi%20International%2C%20explains%3A%20%E2%80%9CIn%20places%20like%20Rajasthan%2C%20rainwater%20harvesting%20ponds%20are%20common%2C%20but%20evaporation%20is%20a%20huge%20problem.%20If%20we%20cover%20these%20ponds%20with%20floating%20solar%20panels%2C%20we%20not%20only%20reduce%20evaporation%20but%20also%20generate%20electricity.%20This%20can%20be%20connected%20to%20a%20village%20microgrid%2C%20providing%20backup%20power%20for%20homes%20or%20for%20irrigation.%E2%80%9D%20(A%20village%20microgrid%20is%20a%20small-scale%20electricity%20network%20that%20can%20operate%20independently%20from%20the%20main%20grid%2C%20ensuring%20power%20even%20during%20outages.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-4-1755164187.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Panels%20block%20sunlight%2C%20cutting%20evaporation%20losses%20by%20up%20to%2090%20percent%20and%20suppressing%20algae%20growth.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-4-1755164187.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-4-1755164187-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-4-1755164187-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-4-1755164187-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-4-1755164187-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-487107%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPanels%20block%20sunlight%2C%20reducing%20evaporation%20losses%20by%20up%20to%2090%20percent%20and%20suppressing%20algae%20growth.%20%3Cem%3EImage%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Ffloating-solar-panel-photovoltaic-pv-system-2493697841%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E%20(For%20representational%20purposes%20only)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20FPV%20pairs%20beautifully%20with%20another%20clean%20power%20source.%20Sanjeev%20Jain%2C%20retired%20chief%20engineer%20(energy%20department)%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFPV%20and%20hydropower%20are%20natural%20allies.%20During%20the%20day%2C%20solar%20can%20supply%20power%2C%20while%20hydropower%20can%20be%20used%20in%20the%20evenings%2C%20creating%20a%20balanced%20generation%20profile.%E2%80%9D%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20two%20work%20in%20tandem%20%E2%80%94%20water-driven%20turbines%20take%20over%20when%20the%20sun%20sets%2C%20ensuring%20a%20steady%20power%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CInstalling%20FPV%20on%20reservoirs%20of%20existing%20hydropower%20plants%20also%20eliminates%20the%20need%20for%20new%20transmission%20infrastructure.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20win-win%20situation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20potential%20is%20already%20being%20tapped%20in%20different%20corners%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20mines%20to%20megawatts%3A%20India%E2%80%99s%20push%20to%20scale%20floating%20solar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20state-run%20power%20giant%2C%20the%20NTPC%2C%20has%20commissioned%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F118786%2Findias-largest-floating-solar-plant-in-kerala-is-now-all-set-for-operations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efloating%20solar%20projects%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Telangana%2C%20Kerala%2C%20and%20several%20more%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Sanjeev%20has%20been%20closely%20involved.%20%E2%80%9CChhattisgarh%20is%20blessed%20with%20numerous%20water%20bodies%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20ideal%20for%20FPV%20systems%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20state%E2%80%99s%20first%20major%20project%2C%20a%2015%20MW%20floating%20solar%20plant%2C%20is%20being%20set%20up%20by%20Steel%20Authority%20of%20India%20Limited%20(SAIL)%E2%80%93Bhilai%20at%20the%20Maroda-1%20reservoir%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20NTPC.%20It%20will%20generate%20about%2034.26%20million%20units%20annually%20for%20captive%20use%20at%20the%20Bhilai%20Steel%20Plant%2C%20helping%20reduce%20its%20carbon%20footprint.%E2%80%9D%20(In%20practice%2C%20this%20means%20the%20plant%20directly%20uses%20the%20generated%20solar%20power%2C%20reducing%20its%20need%20to%20draw%20electricity%20from%20coal-heavy%20state%20grids.)%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjeev%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CApart%20from%20Maroda-1%2C%20NTPC%20has%20projects%20planned%20in%20Korba%20and%20other%20locations.%20We%20have%20mapped%20around%203%2C000%20MW%20of%20FPV%20potential%20across%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20water%20bodies%2C%20including%20a%20single%20site%2C%20Sikassa%20Dam%2C%20with%20a%20staggering%202%2C500%20MW%20potential.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20all%20FPV%20sites%20are%20traditional%20reservoirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20Oriana%20Power%20commissioned%20a%201%20MWp%20floating%20solar%20plant%20for%20Udaipur%20Cement%20Works%20Limited%2C%20not%20on%20a%20river%20or%20lake%2C%20but%20on%20the%20Dabok%20mine%20pond%20%E2%80%94%20a%20deep%20water-filled%20crater%20left%20by%20years%20of%20limestone%20extraction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-1-1755164201.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sanjeev%20Jain%20and%20Harsh%20Tiwari%20have%20been%20working%20in%20the%20renewable%20energy%20space%20for%20decades.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-1-1755164201.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-1-1755164201-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-1-1755164201-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-1-1755164201-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Ffloating-solar-farms-1-1755164201-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-487109%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESanjeev%20Jain%