0Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20VTU%2C%20he%20was%20expected%20to%20take%20up%20a%20secured%20job%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20like%20many%20of%20his%20peers.%20But%20the%20young%20graduate%20had%20other%20plans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELohith%E2%80%99s%20interest%20in%20flowers%20began%20during%20his%20school%20years.%20His%20cousin%2C%20Gopal%20S%20Reddy%2C%20who%20had%20been%20growing%20and%20selling%20flowers%20since%201995%2C%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20sparking%20his%20curiosity.%20When%20his%20cousin%20shifted%20to%20protected%20cultivation%20farming%2C%20he%20was%20actively%20involved%20in%20the%20day-to-day%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20look%20after%20the%20flowers%2C%20see%20how%20they%20grew%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20my%20interest%20in%20commercial%20flower%20farming%20began%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lohith%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20This%20on-ground%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328701%2Fpunjab-farmer-starts-floriculture-exotic-flowers-help-earn-more-profits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperience%20with%20floriculture%3C%2Fa%3E%20spurred%20a%20passion%20that%20later%20defined%20his%20professional%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETrading%20tech%20for%20floriculture%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20Gopal%20began%20cultivating%20roses%20on%20his%20land%2C%20but%20eventually%20moved%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20leaving%20the%20farm%20behind.%20This%20opened%20up%20an%20opportunity%20for%20Lohith%2C%20who%20had%20always%20been%20passionate%20about%20flower%20cultivation%2C%20to%20take%20over%20and%20manage%20the%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20completing%20my%20engineering%2C%20I%20realised%20I%20wanted%20to%20gain%20hands-on%20experience%20in%20flower%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20This%20decision%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20entrepreneur%E2%80%99s%20journey%20into%20the%20world%20of%20flowers.%20While%20continuing%20his%20brother%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F277970%2Ffarmers-grow-roses-earn-lakhs-in-maharashtra-drought-prone-village%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erose%20cultivation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20began%20exploring%20floriculture%20extensively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201976px)%20100vw%2C%201976px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221976%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lohith%20dedicated%20around%204%2C000%20square%20meters%20of%20his%20farm%20to%20chrysanthemums%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654.jpg%201976w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0016_11zon-1735308654-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-393530%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221482%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELohith%20dedicated%20around%204%2C000%20square%20metres%20of%20his%20farm%20to%20chrysanthemums.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Lohith%20took%20his%20first%20major%20step%20into%20commercial%20farming.%20%E2%80%9CI%20built%20my%20farm%20with%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2015%20lakh%2C%20which%20included%20building%20a%20polyhouse%20for%20Rs%208%20lakh%2C%20and%20purchasing%2012%2C000%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F277179%2Fengineer-quits-england-job-gerbera-farming-uttar-pradesh-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egerbera%20plants%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20nursery%20in%20Pune%20for%20Rs%204%20lakh.%20I%20sold%20about%2040%2C000%20to%2050%2C000%20gerbera%20flowers%20per%20month%20in%20the%20Bengaluru%20market%2C%20making%20around%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20monthly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20with%20gerbera%20because%20it%20was%20a%20crop%20that%2C%20if%20properly%20maintained%2C%20could%20yield%20for%20more%20than%20three%20years.%20I%20wanted%20a%20reliable%20source%20of%20income%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20The%20success%20of%20this%20initial%20venture%20gave%20him%20the%20confidence%20to%20diversify%20his%20flower%20farming%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20gerberas%20proved%20to%20be%20successful%2C%20Lohith%20was%20always%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20other%20opportunities%20to%20expand%20his%20flower%20business.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%2C%20I%20realised%20chrysanthemum%20was%20not%20being%20grown%20much.%20Very%20few%20farmers%20were%20growing%20it%2C%20and%20the%20demand%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20that%20high.%20But%20I%20saw%20the%20potential%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20leap%20and%20started%20growing%20chrysanthemums%2C%20alongside%20gerberas.%20%E2%80%9CI%20dedicated%20around%204%2C000%20square%20meters%20of%20my%20farm%20to%20chrysanthemums%20and%20planted%202%2C000%20square%20meters%20of%20gerberas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20His%20instinct%20to%20diversify%20paid%20off.%20Chrysanthemums%20turned%20out%20to%20have%20immense%20market%20potential%2C%20not%20just%20in%20terms%20of%20popularity%20but%20also%20because%20of%20their%20versatility%20in%20colour%20and%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EExperimentation%20and%20a%20quest%20for%20quality%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20growing%20the%20flowers%20presented%20their%20own%20set%20of%20challenges.%20One%20of%20the%20major%20obstructions%20Lohith%20faced%20was%20the%20flower%E2%80%99s%20light%20sensitivity.%20%E2%80%9CChrysanthemum%20is%20a%20light-sensitive%20crop.%20It%20requires%2017-18%20hours%20of%20darkness%2C%20which%20is%20only%20possible%20during%20winter.%20Managing%20this%20in%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20longer%20summer%20days%20was%20a%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20He%20also%20found%20that%20chrysanthemums%20grown%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%20performed%20differently%20in%20terms%20of%20quality%2C%20and%20he%20had%20to%20experiment%20with%20various%20varieties%20like%20pink%20Santini%2C%20yellow%20Santini%2C%20and%20red%20calimero%20to%20find%20the%20best%20fit%20for%20the%20local%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202483px)%20100vw%2C%202483px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FIMG-20241220-WA0014_11zon-1735308878.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222483%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lohith%20sel