2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20blue%20pinkgill%E2%80%99s%20colour%20comes%20from%20azulene%2C%20a%20naturally%20occurring%20blue%20pigment%20also%20found%20in%20some%20flowers%20and%20plants%2C%20but%20rare%20in%20fungi.%20It%E2%80%99s%20what%20gives%20the%20mushroom%20its%20almost%20unreal%20shade%20of%20blue.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20shuttlecock%20mushroom%E2%80%99s%20lattice%20%E2%80%94%20a%20crisscross%2C%20net-like%20structure%20%E2%80%94%20is%20not%20for%20beauty%20alone%3B%20it%20helps%20the%20fungus%20release%20its%20spores%20efficiently%20into%20the%20air.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-13T150051.105-1755077457.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20blue%20pinkgill%20mushroom%20looks%20like%20it%20has%20been%20painted%20straight%20out%20of%20an%20artist%E2%80%99s%20palette.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-13T150051.105-1755077457.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-13T150051.105-1755077457-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-13T150051.105-1755077457-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-13T150051.105-1755077457-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-13T150051.105-1755077457-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-486369%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20blue%20pinkgill%20mushroom%20looks%20like%20i