%3E%20that%20transformed%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20relationship%20with%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20with%20more%20than%20900%20million%20users%2C%20the%20internet%20has%20become%20an%20indispensable%20part%20of%20daily%20life%20for%20Indians.%20It%20shapes%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20from%20banking%20and%20news%20consumption%20to%20entertainment%2C%20online%20shopping%2C%20education%2C%20and%20staying%20connected%20through%20social%20media%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20video%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20internet%2C%20once%20a%20novelty%2C%20is%20now%20a%20necessity%20many%20feel%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20live%20without.%20Yet%20few%20may%20recall%20how%20this%20digital%20revolution%20began%20and%20what%20it%20took%20to%20get%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBefore%20the%20boom%3A%20BBS%20and%20the%20pre-Internet%20era%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20digital%20journey%20started%20much%20earlier%20in%20unexpected%20corners%20%E2%80%94%20often%20in%20the%20homes%20of%20passionate%20students%20and%20techies%2C%20long%20before%20commercial%20networks%20went%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FSuchit-Nanda-of-Nanda-Netcom_11zon-1754993290-500x625.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22internet%20launch%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FSuchit-Nanda-of-Nanda-Netcom_11zon-1754993290-500x625.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FSuchit-Nanda-of-Nanda-Netcom_11zon-1754993290-240x300.jpg%20240w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FSuchit-Nanda-of-Nanda-Netcom_11zon-1754993290-768x960.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FSuchit-Nanda-of-Nanda-Netcom_11zon-1754993290-150x188.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FSuchit-Nanda-of-Nanda-Netcom_11zon-1754993290.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-485561%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22625%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20in%201989%20that%20students%20Suchit%20Nanda%20and%20his%20brother%20Anish%20started%20Live%20Wire!%20BBS%20(LWBBS)%20from%20their%20bedroom%20in%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Powai.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20commercial%20internet%20arrived%20in%20India%2C%20a%20thriving%20BBS%20(Bulletin%20Board%20System)%20community%20existed%2C%20connecting%20computers%20over%20landlines%20and%20modems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%201989%20that%20students%20Suchit%20Nanda%20and%20his%20brother%20Anish%20started%20Live%20Wire!%20BBS%20(LWBBS)%20from%20their%20bedroom%20in%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Powai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELWBBS%20was%20the%20first%20and%20largest%20BBS%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent%2C%20playing%20a%20foundational%20role%20in%20connecting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F180422%2Fpaytm-movie-tickets-internet-handling-fees-rbi-vijay-gopal-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearly%20Indian%20internet%20users%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20fostering%20a%20digital%20community%20before%20internet%20access%20became%20widespread.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20BBS%20became%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20and%20largest%2C%20connecting%20users%20nationwide%20through%20the%20global%20FidoNet%20network.%20This%20led%20to%20my%20participation%20in%20INET%20conferences%2C%20where%20I%20advocated%20for%20public%20internet%20access%20in%20India.%20Given%20the%20security%20policies%20then%2C%20only%20government-linked%20bodies%20could%20launch%20the%20internet.%20VSNL%20was%20ideal%2C%20as%20it%20had%20existing%20lease%20lines%20and%20global%20partnerships.%20This%20led%20to%20meetings%20with%20VSNL%E2%80%99s%20leadership%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20internet%20revolution%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Suchit%20Nanda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENanda%E2%80%99s%20pioneering%20spirit%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20at%20advocacy.%20His%20tech%20firm%20was%20among%20the%20first%20to%20receive%20an%20internet%20licence%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Telecommunications%20(DoT).%20He%20played%20a%20trailblazing%20role%20in%20expanding%20digital%20access%20through%20the%20development%20of%20internet%20set-top%20boxes%20(STBs)%20%E2%80%94%20bringing%20the%20web%20to%20television%20screens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20innovative%20ventures%20like%20Nanda%20Netcom%20and%20Jadoonet.com%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20tech%20giants%20Samsung%20and%20Intel%2C%20he%20helped%20make%20the%20internet%20more%20accessible%20to%20Indian%20households%2C%20redefining%20how%20people%20connected%20and%20consumed%20digital%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20launch%3A%20VSNL%E2%80%99s%20gateway%20to%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Independence%20Day%20in%201995%2C%20the%20GIAS%20public%20internet%20service%20by%20VSNL%20was%20launched%20and%20opened%20to%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FNeeraj-Sonker-Pic-Coutesy-constl.com_11zon-1754993300-500x533.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22internet%20launch%20in%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FNeeraj-Sonker-Pic-Coutesy-constl.com_11zon-1754993300-500x533.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FNeeraj-Sonker-Pic-Coutesy-constl.com_11zon-1754993300-281x300.jpg%20281w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%