2C%20Kolkata%2C%20and%20Pune.%20A%20couple%20of%20weeks%20later%2C%20Bangalore%20was%20added%20to%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERetail%20customers%20received%20dial-up%20services%2C%20while%20enterprises%20were%20offered%20leased%20line%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20dial-up%20capacity%20was%20limited%20to%20just%2016%20or%2032%20lines%2C%20and%20we%20had%20access%20to%20only%20four%20Class%20C%20IP%20addresses%20from%20APNIC%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Neeraj%20Sonker%2C%20who%20served%20as%20General%20Manager%2C%20Internet%20Services%20at%20VSNL%20from%201994%20to%202000%2C%20in%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%20marking%20the%20silver%20jubilee%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20internet%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EScaling%20up%3A%20from%20metro%20cities%20to%20tier%202%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F139241%2Fvoip-calls-clearer-internet-telecom-sync-ist%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Department%20of%20Telecommunications%20(DoT)%20%3C%2Fa%3Edirected%20VSNL%20to%20extend%20internet%20services%20to%20Tier%202%20cities%2C%20beginning%20with%20state%20capitals.%20Starting%20in%201996%2C%20VSNL%20began%20rolling%20out%20internet%20access%20across%20these%20regional%20hubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonkar%E2%80%99s%20account%20of%20the%20period%20provides%20insights%20into%20the%20technical%20and%20operational%20challenges%20faced%2C%20including%20scaling%20infrastructure%20to%20meet%20skyrocketing%20demand%20and%20addressing%20customer%20and%20media%20criticism%20in%20the%20early%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20highlights%20how%2C%20despite%20limited%20network%20expertise%20and%20resources%2C%20the%20team%20managed%20to%20connect%20major%20cities%20through%20a%2064-kbps%20satellite%20link%2C%20established%20Points%20of%20Presence%20(POPs)%20across%20India%2C%20provided%20dial-up%20and%20leased%20line%20services%2C%20and%20later%20expanded%20the%20network%20to%20Tier%202%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20leadership%20also%20saw%20the%20rollout%20of%20key%20innovations%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20shift%20from%20static%20to%20dynamic%20network%20routing%20and%20improvements%20in%20customer%20support%20and%20billing%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20users%3A%20The%20internet%20guide%20and%20community%20building%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20team%20continued%20to%20upgrade%20infrastructure%20and%20expand%20services%2C%20attention%20increasingly%20turned%20to%20empowering%20customers%20to%20navigate%20the%20new%20digital%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20pivotal%20initiative%20in%20this%20direction%20was%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20Internet%20User%20Guide%20(The%20Guide)%2C%20which%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20both%20customers%20and%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20the%20need%20for%20user%20empowerment%2C%20the%20team%2C%20at%20Nanda%E2%80%99s%20suggestion%2C%20enlisted%20Stanford%20Professor%20Dr%20Raj%20Mehta%20to%20craft%20the%20Internet%20User%20Guide.%20Dr%20Mehta%E2%80%99s%20hands-on%20approach%20%E2%80%94%20fielding%20late-night%20calls%20and%20emails%20from%20users%20nationwide%20%E2%80%94%20reflected%20the%20spirit%20of%20collaboration%20at%20the%20dawn%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20digital%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Mehta%20returned%20to%20India%20during%20that%20time%20and%20dedicated%20significant%20effort%20to%20assisting%20VSNL%20and%20end-users.%20In%201997%2C%20the%20spiral-bound%20book%20was%20published.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-15-1754993306.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.